<H3> <TI>   Rybkin Meets Slovak National Council Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rybkin Meets Slovak National Council Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2405103194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1021 GMT 24 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2405103194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow May 24 ITAR-TASS -- State Duma Speaker Ivan 
Rybkin on Tuesday received a Slovak National Council delegation 
led by Ivan Laluga, chairman of the Foreign Policy Committee, 
the Duma press service announced. 
  The two sides discussed prospects for an improvement and 
development of mutually beneficial contacts between Russia and 
Slovakia in the economic, scientific and cultural fields, 
pointing out the importance of developing interparliamentary 
contacts. 
  Laluga conveyed an official invitation from the chairman of 
the National Council of the Slovak Republic to the State Duma 
speaker to visit Slovakia at the head of a Russian parliamentary 
delegation. 

</TEXT>

