<H3> <TI>   Russian Minister Calls for Ending Sanctions on Abkhazia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Minister Calls for Ending Sanctions on Abkhazia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2305135894 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1100 GMT 23 May 94 </F>
