<H3> <TI>   Oleynik Says Talks With Crimea Proceeding Normally </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Oleynik Says Talks With Crimea Proceeding Normally </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2405110794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1103 GMT 24 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2405110794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
