<H3> <TI>   Talks Set Terms for Russian Use of Military Facilities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Talks Set Terms for Russian Use of Military Facilities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS2505080794 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 0300 
