rubric: "Are Chechens To Make Friends with Cossacks?"] 
  [Text] President of the Chechen Republic Dzhokhar Dudayev 
has proposed to the Terek Cossacks that both cooperate for the 
sake of peace and order in the Caucasus. 
  At his latest meeting with Terek Cossack Hetman Vasiliy 
Starodubtsev in Groznyy, he stated that there have not been and 
there still are no real conflicts between Chechens and Cossacks 
and they could definitely present a united front to resolve the 
majority of their problems. Representatives of the Terek 
Cossacks invited the Chechen president to their Great Assembly 
which will take place in the city of Kizlyar 28 May. 

