  According to the Abkhazian representatives, more than 250 
shells and mortars were fired at the Abkhazian positions on 
Tuesday. The shelling began at 18:20 and stopped at 22:30, and 
resulted in the wounding of four Abkhazian military personnel. 

</TEXT>

